loaded baked potato i am looking for a good loaded baked potato recipe any ideas where i can get one at loaded twice baked potatoes ingredients medium russet potatoes ounces lean ground beef cup broccoli florets finely chopped cup water cup reduced fat cheddar cheese divided cup reduced fat sour cream teaspoon salt teaspoon freshly ground pepper scallions sliced preparation pierce potatoes all over with a fork place in the microwave and cook at power turning once or twice until the potatoes are soft about minutes or use the potato setting on your microwave and cook according to the manufacturer s instructions meanwhile brown meat in a large skillet over medium high heat stirring often about minutes transfer to a large bowl increase heat to high add broccoli and water to the skillet cover and cook until tender to minutes drain the broccoli add to the meat carefully cut off the top third of the cooked potatoes reserve the tops for another use scoop the insides out into a medium bowl place the potato shells in a small baking dish add cup cheddar sour cream salt and pepper to the potato insides and mash with a fork or potato masher add scallions and the potato mixture to the broccoli and meat stir to combine evenly divide the potato mixture among the potato shells and top with the remaining cup cheese microwave on high until the filling is hot and the cheese is melted to minutes vegetarian variation replace the ground beef with a soy based substitute or omit the beef altogether and increase the broccoli to cups and the cheese to cups delicious recipe enjoy Pizza Jewish cuisine Peruvian cuisine Ice cream Breakfast Bread Recipe Idli Kraft Dinner French cuisine In-N-Out Burger Cantonese cuisine Bengali cuisine Potato chips Russian cuisine Pancake Cuisine of Brazil German cuisine Pie Korean cuisine Cuisine of Malaysia Sandwich Vegetarian cuisine Ramen MRE Domesticated turkey Rice pudding Food Cincinnati chili Apple pie Polish cuisine Coffee Risotto Kosher foods D__ner kebab